Creative director Simone Bellotti had an amazing ascent at Bally, the
Swiss leather goods house. But he seemed destined for poaching, and now wor=
d in Milan is that he=E2=80=99s on to his next =E2=80=9Cproject=E2=80=9D=E2=
=80=94with roads pointing to Jil Sander.

Lauren Sherman ( https://puck.news/author/lauren-sherman/?utm_campaign=3DLi=
ne+Sheet+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%281%2F22%2F25%29&utm_content=3DLine+Sheet+-+SUBSCRI=
